            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Mix soy sauce, maple syrup, garlic and onion together in a small oven dish."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Put the salmon in a shallow dish and spoon the marinade over it. The salmon should fill the dish and the marinade come about ½ way up the salmon so it doesn’t dry out during cooking. If it doesn’t, I’ll often just add a little extra soy sauce."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Leave for 10-30 minutes to marinate."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Bake at gas 7 for about ½ hour. It should be cooked after around 15mins but you’re looking for the top of the salmon to caramelise."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
